						               													<description>From the Kickstarter page:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Legends of the American Frontier True Grit Expansion will add dozens of extra cards, as well as an awesome set of 15 metal True Grit tokens to replace those in the base game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What's Your Legend?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Back East:&amp;#10;Legend: Appointed by President of United States to negotiate treaty to end the War of 1812.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 3 VP Solo Adventure. Skills: Knowledge + Personality = 20 Rewards: 2 Status + 1 Fame&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flavor Text: Travel to Ghent, Belgium to lead the treaty negotiations that end the war of 1812.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Legend: Architect of the Treaty with Creek Nation&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 1 VP Group Adventure. Skills: Frontier OR Personality = 35, Rewards: Skill and 2 Status / 1 Fame OR 1 Status&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flavor Text: Traded southern land in Georgia to Creek Nation for return of harbored slaves.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Legend: Heroic Soldier in the Battle of Fallen Timbers against the Shawnee and Delaware&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 3VP Solo Adventure. Skills: Combat 18,   Rewards: Skill + 2 Fame OR 2 Status&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flavor Text: Fight the Shawnee and Delaware lead by Blue Jacket for disputed Ohio Territory&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Frontier:&amp;#10;Legend: Piloted the first Steamboat (or Riverboat) down the Mississippi &amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 2 VP Solo Adventure. Skills: Knowledge = 15 Rewards: +1 Fame + 1 Wealth and + 1 Happiness or +1 Status&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flavor Text: First to Pilot Steamboat (or Riverboat) from Minneapolis to New Orleans&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Far West:&amp;#10;Legend: Discovered the comstock lode creating the Virginia City Boomtown.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 2 VP. Solo Adventure: Skills: Frontier + Knowledge = 18 Rewards: 3 Wealth +1 Fame&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flavor Text: Discover Gold, sparking a Boomtown in Nevada.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Legend: Key member of the Pike Expedition's Climb of Grand Peak&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 3VP Group Adventure. Skills: Capitalism OR Frontier OR Knowledge = 60, Rewards: Skill + 2 Fame + 1 Status / 2 Fame / 2 Fame + 1 Hardship&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flavor Text: Aided Lieutenant Pike during his explorations of the Louisiana Purchase&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
